rder-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;通过PLM规划项目来衔接核心PLM能力建设和IPD流程导入，能够更快更好地将IPD项目业务收益体现到维力的研发实践中去。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');
INSERT INTO `ey_cases_content` VALUES ('11', '179', '1573461576', '1573461576', '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 26px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;近年来，热浇道系统使用阀式浇口设计的比例持续成长，其应用领域也逐渐扩大中，从汽车、电子到医疗等产业都可以看到使用阀式热浇道系统的案例。阀式浇口设计具备许多生产优势，浇口平整、不需要等待浇口固化等可以提升产品外观质量与有效缩短成型周期。阀式浇口另一项重要的优势为可以结合时序控制技术来控制浇口开启时机，有效解决产品表面结合线问题。然而时序控制技术也面临应用上的挑战。随着射出成型的充填比例增加，射出压力也会跟着上升以符合充填流率，热流道内部会累积一定压力范围。当关闭中的阀式浇口快速开启时，瞬间压力释放使融胶以高速进入模腔，这时会造成塑件表面发生质量不一的缺陷，如：流痕、光泽不均匀…等问题，对产品良率产生严重影响。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 26px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;为了协助热浇道使用者将时序控制技术的效益发挥至更大，达到提升塑件质量目标，热浇道厂商推出可对阀针开关浇口做速度控制的新解决方案，Moldex3D也因应市场的需求，在进阶热流道解决方案研发「阀针作动速度控制仿真技术」，让分析工程师可以从Moldex3D中选择使用一般或进阶阀式浇口控制 (图一)；若选择进阶阀式浇口模拟分析，设计者可以针对阀针上下作动的速度进行控制调整 (图二)。从图三可以看到，浇口区域的速度场因为阀针的位置改变而产生变化，再搭配充填流动分析结果可以验证阀针速度控制对流动波前的影响和改善效果 (图四)，确保表面流痕问题获得显著改善。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-1.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-0&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter wp-image-28884 &quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-1&quot; width=&quot;471&quot; height=&quot;322&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 5px auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;图一 &amp;nbsp;Moldex3D提供一般阀浇口分析(左)以及进阶阀式浇口控制分析(右)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-2.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-1&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; wp-image-28885 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-2&quot; width=&quot;397&quot; height=&quot;460&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 5px auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;图二 &amp;nbsp;Moldex3D仿真阀针移动速度控制的设定接口&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-3.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-2&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; wp-image-28886 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-3&quot; width=&quot;569&quot; height=&quot;166&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 5px auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;图三 &amp;nbsp;阀针作动对浇口的速度场产生变化&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-4.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-3&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; wp-image-28887&quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-4.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-4&quot; width=&quot;312&quot; height=&quot;104&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;　　&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-5.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-4&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; wp-image-28888&quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-5.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-5&quot; width=&quot;314&quot; height=&quot;98&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;图四 &amp;nbsp;利用Moldex3D仿真验证阀针速度控制技术&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;左：多浇口、时序进浇设计容易产生流痕&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;右：搭配阀针速度控制技术后，表面流痕问题获得显著改善&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 26px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;除此之外，在网格前处理阶段，Moldex3D使用者可以藉由原本的网格编辑工具(图五)，依照实际的阀式浇口几何形状进行建模，包含：热流道几何、阀针几何、行程距离、浇口控制编号…等等。产品设计者不需要进行几何简化，牺牲重要几何信息，透过真实三维实体网格技术，Moldex3D模流分析完整考虑更真实的阀式浇口设计，大幅提升模拟分析的准确度。在成型条件设定阶段，产品设计者还可以针对各别浇口群组进行控制，例如：浇口初始状态(开或关)、阀针移动速度、速度段数等，对于有阀式浇口进阶模拟需求的使用者，是不可或缺的利器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-6.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-5&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; wp-image-28893 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-6.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-6&quot; width=&quot;603&quot; height=&quot;283&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 5px auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;图五 &amp;nbsp;Moldex3D 提供网格编辑工具，让使用者依照实际阀式浇口几何形状进行建模&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 26px; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;热浇道系统已经是塑料射出成型制程中不可或缺的重要设计之一，业界也仍持续投入研究资源发展更先进、更广范的应用。透过Moldex3D仿真及验证阀针速度控制技术，热浇道使用者可以在实际开发前进行设计验证和优化，降低塑件表面发生瑕疵的机会，将时序控制技术效益发挥至更大，确实为产品质量把关。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Meiryo, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-7.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;shadowbox[sbpost-28883];player=img;&quot; data-rel=&quot;lightbox-image-6&quot; data-rl_title=&quot;&quot; data-rl_caption=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(195, 43, 7);&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; wp-image-28894 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://www.moldex3d.com/en/assets/2015/09/use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-7.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;use-moldex3ds-new-pin-movement-analysis-technology-to-yield-greater-process-gains-7&quot; width=&quot;615&quot; height=&quot;441&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 5px auto;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;图六 &amp;nbsp;使用阀针作动功能进行浇口时序控制的案例&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
INSERT INTO `ey_cases_content` VALUES ('13', '183', '1577511719', '1577511719', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;项目背景&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;广州万宝集团有限公司（以下简称“广州万宝集团”）是以制冷产品、家用电器研发、生产、安装及销售；资本投资及管理；商业贸易为三大主业的大型现代化综合性集团公司，公司注册资金 93393万元，拥有广州人和、从化、番禺及青岛、合肥、海宁、民权以及意大利ACC等八大生产基地。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;广州万宝集团是中国家电行业中最早、最具规模的家电制冷设备和产品研发制造中心，现建有国家级企业技术中心、CNAS国家认可实验室和广东省工程技术研究开发中心，设立了博士后科研工作站。凭借三十年多来在家电、制冷领域积累的丰富的研发生产经验，本着以人才为本，以顾客满意为事业基石的宗旨，努力为社会创造最优质的产品。主要产品包括冰箱、冷柜、空调（家用、商用、中央）、太阳能及热泵热水器（家用、商用）、家庭用小电器，制冷压缩机及配套产品等，形成了中国最完整的制冷设备产业链及家电系列产品集群，具有产品系列化以及在规模和技术上强大的优势。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;万宝存在多地的研发中心，多个生产基地间需要协同开发和共享数据，这样就对原有的离散性的研发体系提出挑战，万宝希望建立一套统一的研发平台，支撑集团下多个基地的研发及其生产基地对研发数据的使用，加强产品开发中的管理，提高开发质量和速度来获得竞争优势。为此，经过为期半年的全面考察，万宝集团最终选择阳普科技作为PLM项目合作伙伴，于2011年正式启动PLM项目。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Lucida Grande&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;wenquanyi micro hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191112/1-1911121JG1S5.jpg&quot; title=&quot;万宝集团Windchill PLM项目案例分享(图1)&quot; alt=&quot;1-1911121JG1S5.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;企业面临的挑战与需求&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;目前冰箱行业的竞争激烈，耗电量的指标不断下降，而冰箱节能主要靠压缩机，市场也不断要求产品变化要快，所以对于万宝压缩机来说，需要面临以下问题:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.2em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;产品上市的速度要快，需要加强产品开发中的管理，提高开发质量和速度来获得竞争优势。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;由于市场要求交货期要快，目前产品很多来不及做验证就上市，如果出货后发现有问题，可能会以冰箱的十倍价格进行罚款，这方面存在隐患。需要通过标准化的设计和重用，减少后续被迫以工艺保证的方式来保证质量，从而延误交期的做法。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;明年的产能要做到1500万台压缩机，所以现场的图纸管理很重要，一天将近生产7万台，如果出了问题，返工的时间费用和成本费用都会很高。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;根据集团的发展，广压华光研究院需要与青岛合肥等生产基地共享一些开发数据，共同保证企业的销售生产目标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;在PLM一期项目的规划里，集团技术中心，广压研究院，青岛和合肥生产基地都纳入到系统的实施范围内。这几个研发单位对PLM系统支持的业务各有差别，广压研究院对设计重用的要求较多，生产多为量产，涉及工艺和材料成本的生产要求，并且需要与青岛合肥等生产基地共享一些开发数据；集团技术中心主要是作为企业孵化器为相关企业提供技术资料，不涉及工艺和生产，较少设计重用，以小批试制居多，主要关注前沿技术的研发和实现，对工艺是否适宜量产、材料是否经济等生产方面的要求则较为次要。青岛生产基地有自己的研发中心，有部分产品设计是需要参考广州的广压研究院。合肥生产基地没有研发，但是需要查看各种研发中心提供的图纸。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;通过PTC Windchill PLM 这个系统平台，能有效解决万宝所面临的以上问题，并且系统强大的功能足以支撑万宝目前及未来的复杂的业务要求。系统通过标准化设计快速进行重用，提升设计效率，打通和管控产品研发各数据的产生、签审、变更以及发布过程，建立一个跨区域，异地的，统一的，准确的产品数据管理平台。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;应用效应&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;在实施Windchill PLM 系统后，万宝集团获得了如下的效益提升：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.2em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;构建完全电子化的，集中统一的文档资料管控和协同平台，改变产品图纸、技术资料存放混乱的情况，实现真正的权限控制范围内的文件共享，方便、快速地查询技术资料；缩短设计知识的查找时间，提高设计研发效率。现在，无论是在广州基地，还是青岛基地，都实现了无纸化和文档电子签审，提高了图文档的管理效率多达40%。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;建立起以产品结构为核心的产品数据存储和管理体系。有效管理系列化产品的复杂变型，目前，广压设计院的一个压缩机系列的设计，超过100+的产品实例，产品的设计变更频繁，利用标准系统化的方法，快速派生衍生产品实例，减少产品设计、变型的周期，满足客户的个性化需求，加快产品投放市场的速度；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;建立并优化符合质量体系的产品研发流程管理系统，有效控制产品研发演变过程中不同阶段的产品质量；我们为万宝设计了很多定制化的流程，在保证产品质量的前提下支持了流程上的柔性控制。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;有效管理产品发展演变历史，实现设计更改的有效控制，满足对更改历史的追溯要求，维护产品数据一致性，提高产品开发质量；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; wo